(43,3,11,'<h2 class=\"sb_title\">Need Help?</h2>\n<p>We''ve designed the steps below to help you get oriented with Movie Say.So. If you find you need additional help, please don''t hesitate to <a href=\"mailto:movie@say.so\">contact us</a>.</p>\n<div class=\"sb_tabs\">\n	<ul>\n		<li><a href=\"#onboard_tabs_1\">Welcome!</a></li>\n		<li><a href=\"#onboard_tabs_2\">What Can I Do?</a></li>\n		<li><a href=\"#onboard_tabs_3\">What Do I Get?</a></li>\n		<li><a href=\"#onboard_tabs_4\">Get Started</a></li>\n		<li style=\"display:none;\"><a href=\"#onboard_tabs_5\"> </a></li>\n	</ul>\n\n	<div id=\"onboard_tabs_1\" class=\"sb_tabPane\">\n		<h3 class=\"sb_title\" align=\"center\" style=\"font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 10px\">Congratulations and Thank You!</h3>\n		<p align=\"center\"><big>By becoming a member of Movie Say.So, you''ve achieved level 1, and earned 1000 CineStars and 75 CineBucks.</big></p>\n		<br />\n		<ul class=\"sb_lineList\">\n			<li class=\"sb_img_experience\"><strong class=\"sb_theme_textHighlight\">\"CineStars\"</strong> show your level of influence in the Movie Say.So community. You earn them for sharing your expertise, experience and opinions. Your <strong class=\"sb_theme_textHighlight\">CineStars</strong> determine your access to higher levels of access and influence.</li>\n			<li class=\"sb_img_redeemable\"><strong class=\"sb_theme_textHighlight\">\"CineBucks\"</strong> are the virtual currency of Movie Say.So. Nearly about everything you do in the community earns you CineBucks, which can be exchanged for cool movie items in the <a class=\"sb_nav_element\" rel=\"sb_popBox_rewards\" href=\"//%CONFIG_BASE_DOMAIN%/starbar/content/rewards\">Rewards Center</a>.</li>\n		</ul>\n	</div><!-- #tab_1 -->\n	<div id=\"onboard_tabs_2\" class=\"sb_tabPane\">\n		<h3 class=\"sb_title\" align=\"center\">Give Your Opinion, Share It and Earn!</h3>\n		<p align=\"center\">Your point of view and opinion are invaluable. Express yourself through fun polls and surveys, and earn points by rating videos.</p>\n		<ul class=\"sb_lineList\">\n			<li class=\"sb_img_polls\"><strong class=\"sb_theme_textHighlight\">Polls</strong> are quick hits of opinion we''d like you to share. Answer as many or as few as you''d like, and for each one we;ll drop a little something in your Movie Say.So wallet. Every day you''ll get new polls to show off your movie knowledge so be sure to check back often.</li>\n			<li class=\"sb_img_surveys\"><strong class=\"sb_theme_textHighlight\">Surveys</strong> are the big money opportunities. These are important efforts to gauge how we are doing, and we''ll make sure you are compensated accordingly.</li>\n			<li class=\"sb_img_quizzes\"><strong class=\"sb_theme_textHighlight\">Spotlight - </strong>Rate movie trailers and videos; share them to Facebook or Twitter and we''ll compensate you with CineBucks and CineStars. No purchase necessary.</li>\n		</ul>\n	</div><!-- #tab_2 -->\n	<div id=\"onboard_tabs_3\" class=\"sb_tabPane\">\n		<h3 class=\"sb_title\" align=\"center\">Here''s What You Get.</h3>\n		<p align=\"center\">Give us your opinion on movies, celebrities, and what''s going on in Hollywood and you''ll earn CineBucks, our virtual currency that you can redeem for prizes and opportunities.</p>\n		<ul class=\"sb_lineList\">\n			<li class=\"sb_img_prizes\"><strong class=\"sb_theme_textHighlight\">Great Prizes.</strong> Almost everything you do as a Say.So movie buff earns you CineBucks. Exchange them for prizes in the Say.So Rewards Center, which is geared towards movie lovers like you.</li>\n			<li class=\"sb_img_giveaways\">You can also redeem your CineBucks for <strong class=\"sb_theme_textHighlight\">entry tokens for our special giveaways</strong>. The more tokens you get, the better your odds of winning.</li>\n		</ul>\n	</div><!-- #tab_3 -->\n	<div id=\"onboard_tabs_4\" class=\"sb_tabPane\">\n		<h3 class=\"sb_title\" align=\"center\">Okay, Let''s Get Started!</h3>\n		<p align=\"center\" style=\"margin-top: 15px;\"><a href=\"//%CONFIG_BASE_DOMAIN%/starbar/content/embed-survey?survey_id=%CONFIG_PROFILE_SURVEY_ID%\" class=\"sb_nav_element\" rel=\"sb_popBox_surveys_hg\"><img src=\"//%CONFIG_BASE_DOMAIN%/images/movie/img_profile-survey.png\" alt=\"Take the Profile Survey\" /></a><br /><strong>Completing the Profile Survey takes a minute, but we will reward you with a hefty amount of CineBucks and grant you automatic access to our giveaways.</strong></p>\n		<br />\n		<br />\n		<h2 align=\"center\">Already taken the Profile Survey?<br />Check out some quick-hit activities.</h2>\n		<p align=\"center\" style=\"margin-top: 10px;\">\n			<a href=\"//%CONFIG_BASE_DOMAIN%/starbar/content/polls\" class=\"sb_nav_element\" rel=\"sb_popBox_polls\"><img src=\"//%CONFIG_BASE_DOMAIN%/images/movie/img_badge_polls.png\" alt=\"Polls\" style=\"margin: 0px 10px;\" /></a>\n			<a href=\"//%CONFIG_BASE_DOMAIN%/starbar/content/surveys\" class=\"sb_nav_element\" rel=\"sb_popBox_surveys\"><img src=\"//%CONFIG_BASE_DOMAIN%/images/movie/img_badge_surveys.png\" alt=\"Surveys\" style=\"margin: 0px 10px;\" /></a>\n			<a href=\"//%CONFIG_BASE_DOMAIN%/starbar/content/spotlight\" class=\"sb_nav_element\" rel=\"sb_popBox_spotlight\"><img src=\"//%CONFIG_BASE_DOMAIN%/images/movie/img_badge_trailers.png\" alt=\"Trailers\" style=\"margin: 0px 10px;\" /></a>\n		</p>\n	</div><!-- #tab_4 -->\n	<div id=\"onboard_tabs_5\" class=\"sb_tabPane\">\n		<p>\n			<label><strong>Name</strong></label> <input type=\"text\" />\n		</p>\n		<p>\n			<label><strong>Email</strong></label> <input type=\"text\" />\n		</p>\n		<p>\n			<label><strong>Question</strong></label> <textarea rows=\"5\"></textarea>\n		</p>\n		<p>\n			<input type=\"submit\" class=\"sb_theme_button\" value=\"Send\" />\n		</p>\n	</div><!-- #tab_5 -->\n</div><!-- .sb_tabs -->\n'),
