(45,5,11,'<h2 class=\"sb_title\">Need Help?</h2>\n<p>We designed the steps below to help you get oriented with Social Say.So. If you find you need additional help, feel free to <a href=\"mailto:social@say.so\">contact us</a>.</p>\n<div class=\"sb_tabs\">\n	<ul>\n		<li><a href=\"#onboard_tabs_1\">Welcome!</a></li>\n		<li><a href=\"#onboard_tabs_2\">What Can I Do?</a></li>\n		<li><a href=\"#onboard_tabs_3\">What Do I Get?</a></li>\n		<li><a href=\"#onboard_tabs_4\">Get Started</a></li>\n		<li style=\"display:none;\"><a href=\"#onboard_tabs_5\"> </a></li>\n	</ul>\n\n	<div id=\"onboard_tabs_1\" class=\"sb_tabPane\">\n		<h3 class=\"sb_title\" align=\"center\" style=\"font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 10px\">Congratulations and Thank You!</h3>\n		<h3>If you find you need additional help, feel free to <a href=\"mailto:social@say.so\">contact us</a>.</h3>\n		<p align=\"center\"><big>By becoming a member of Social Say.So, you''ve achieved the level \"Spectator\", and earned extra Social SaySo and PaySos.</big></p>\n		<br />\n		<ul class=\"sb_lineList\">\n\n			<li class=\"sb_img_experience\"><strong class=\"sb_theme_textHighlight\">''Social SaySo''</strong> is the currency of influence. You get SaySo by sharing your expertise, experience and opinion, and your Social SaySo determines your access to increasingly important levels of access and influence.</li>\n\n			<li class=\"sb_img_redeemable\"><strong class=\"sb_theme_textHighlight\">\"PaySos\"</strong> are almost as good as cash. Virtually everything you do earns you PaySos, which can be redeemed for all manner of goodies from Say.So. (<a class=\"sb_nav_element\" rel=\"sb_popBox_rewards\" href=\"//%CONFIG_BASE_DOMAIN%/starbar/content/rewards\">see the Rewards Center</a>)</li>\n		</ul>\n	</div><!-- #tab_1 -->\n	<div id=\"onboard_tabs_2\" class=\"sb_tabPane\">\n		<h3 class=\"sb_title\" align=\"center\">Give Your Opinion, Share It and Earn!</h3>\n		<p align=\"center\">Your point of view and opinion are invaluable. Express yourself through fun polls and surveys, and earn Social SaySo and PaySos by completing Social Say.So missions.</p>\n		<ul class=\"sb_lineList\">\n			<li class=\"sb_img_polls\"><strong class=\"sb_theme_textHighlight\">Polls</strong> are quick hits of opinion we''d like you to share. Answer as many or as few as you''d like, and for each one we''ll drop a little something in your Social Say.So wallet.</li>\n			<li class=\"sb_img_surveys\"><strong class=\"sb_theme_textHighlight\">Surveys</strong> are the big money opportunities. These are important efforts to gauge how we are doing, and we''ll make sure you are compensated accordingly.</li>\n			<li class=\"sb_img_quizzes\"><strong class=\"sb_theme_textHighlight\">Missions</strong> are multistage polls, quizzes and surveys that unlock exclusive badges, rewards and content.</li>\n		</ul>\n	</div><!-- #tab_2 -->\n	<div id=\"onboard_tabs_3\" class=\"sb_tabPane\">\n		<h3 class=\"sb_title\" align=\"center\">Here''s What You Get.</h3>\n		<p align=\"center\">Give us your opinion on social and casual gaming and you''ll earn Social PaySos, virtual currency redeemable for prizes and opportunities.</p>\n		<ul class=\"sb_lineList\">\n			<li class=\"sb_img_prizes\"><strong class=\"sb_theme_textHighlight\">Great Prizes.</strong> Almost everything you do as a Social Say.So member earns you PaySos. Use these to redeem prizes from the Rewards Center.<br /></li>\n			<li class=\"sb_img_giveaways\"><strong class=\"sb_theme_textHighlight\">A Chance To Win Prize Giveaways.</strong> Redeem your PaySos for entry tokens for our giveaways. Buy as many entry tokens for each giveaway as you want and increase your odds of winning.</li>\n		</ul>\n	</div><!-- #tab_3 -->\n	<div id=\"onboard_tabs_4\" class=\"sb_tabPane\">\n		<h3 class=\"sb_title\" align=\"center\">Okay, Let''s Get Started!</h3>\n		<p align=\"center\" style=\"margin-top: 15px;\"><a href=\"//%CONFIG_BASE_DOMAIN%/starbar/content/embed-survey?survey_id=%CONFIG_PROFILE_SURVEY_ID%\" class=\"sb_nav_element\" rel=\"sb_popBox_surveys_hg\"><img src=\"//%CONFIG_BASE_DOMAIN%/images/social/img_profile-survey.png\" alt=\"Take the Profile Survey\" /></a><br /><strong>Completing the Profile Survey takes a minute, but we will reward you with a hefty number of Social PaySos and grant you automatic access to our giveaways.</strong></p>\n		<br />\n		<br />\n		<h2 align=\"center\">Not ready to take the Profile Survey?<br />Check out some quick-hit activities.</h2>\n		<p align=\"center\" style=\"margin-top: 10px;\">\n			<a href=\"//%CONFIG_BASE_DOMAIN%/starbar/content/polls\" class=\"sb_nav_element\" rel=\"sb_popBox_polls\"><img src=\"//%CONFIG_BASE_DOMAIN%/images/social/img_badge_polls.png\" alt=\"Polls\" style=\"margin: 0px 10px;\" /></a>\n			<a href=\"//%CONFIG_BASE_DOMAIN%/starbar/content/surveys\" class=\"sb_nav_element\" rel=\"sb_popBox_surveys\"><img src=\"//%CONFIG_BASE_DOMAIN%/images/social/img_badge_surveys.png\" alt=\"Surveys\" style=\"margin: 0px 10px;\" /></a>\n			<a href=\"//%CONFIG_BASE_DOMAIN%/starbar/content/spotlight\" class=\"sb_nav_element\" rel=\"sb_popBox_spotlight\"><img src=\"//%CONFIG_BASE_DOMAIN%/images/social/img_badge_trailers.png\" alt=\"Trailers\" style=\"margin: 0px 10px;\" /></a>\n		</p>\n	</div><!-- #tab_4 -->\n	<div id=\"onboard_tabs_5\" class=\"sb_tabPane\">\n		<p>\n			<label><strong>Name</strong></label> <input type=\"text\" />\n		</p>\n		<p>\n			<label><strong>Email</strong></label> <input type=\"text\" />\n		</p>\n		<p>\n			<label><strong>Question</strong></label> <textarea rows=\"5\"></textarea>\n		</p>\n		<p>\n			<input type=\"submit\" class=\"sb_theme_button\" value=\"Send\" />\n		</p>\n	</div><!-- #tab_5 -->\n</div><!-- .sb_tabs -->\n'),
