(47,3,12,'<h2 class=\"sb_title\">FAQ</h2>\n<p>\n	<strong>What is Movie Say.So?</strong><br />\n	Members of Movie Say.So are rewarded for their film fandom by answering polls, participating in surveys, and rating new and retro movie trailers. Members gain \"CineStars\" (experience points) and \"CineBucks\" (currency). CineBucks can be redeemed for rewards and \"Entry Tokens\" into giveaways.\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/KNaagZ\" target=\"_blank\">(more...)</a>\n</p>\n<p>\n	<strong>Do I have to pay for anything? Is there any shipping & handling fees for prizes obtained or won?</strong><br />\n	No, this is completely free to you. The only thing we want you to do is participate.\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/KfqO67\" target=\"_blank\">(more...)</a>\n</p>\n<p>\n	<strong>What are CineStars used for?</strong><br />\n	CineStars are the equivalent of experience points and determine your level of influence and involvement. Gaining CineStars will increase your Movie Say.So level.\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/JU4l1U\" target=\"_blank\">(more...)</a>\n</p>\n<p>\n	<strong>What are CineBucks used for?</strong><br />\n	CineBucks are the currency you earn by participating in polls, answering surveys, and sharing your ideas. In fact, virtually everything you do in Movie Say.So will earn you CineBucks. CineBucks can be exchanged for various prizes and Entry Tokens in the Reward Center.\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/KfqV1v\" target=\"_blank\">(more...)</a>\n</p>\n<p>\n	<strong>What are Entry Tokens?</strong><br />\n	 Entry Tokens are your way of entering prize giveaways. Users that have purchased an Entry Token with their CineBucks will be entered to win the giveaway. At the end of each giveaway period a prize will be given away to a user that has purchased an Entry Token for the giveaway. You can buy as many Entry Tokens as you want to increase your chance of winning.\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/LxoojL\" target=\"_blank\">(more...)</a>\n</p>\n<p>\n	<strong>Do you really give away the prizes?</strong><br />\n	YES! Every prize that is won will be shipped within 4-6 weeks. Users and fans of Movie Say.So will get the prizes for playing, not the CEO''s nephew or cousin. At the end of each giveaway we will send out an email to all the Movie Say.So users, letting you know who the lucky player is.\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/KaKhtn\" target=\"_blank\">(more...)</a>\n</p>\n<p>\n	<strong>How do I get my prize?</strong><br />\n	When you win a prize we will contact you by email to get the information and mailing address needed to send the prize to you.\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/KMg55A\" target=\"_blank\">(more...)</a>\n</p>\n<p>\n	<strong>Are there any geographic restrictions for playing??</strong><br />\n	Yes, you must reside in the USA to redeem points for prizes. Unfortunately, we cannot ship items out of the USA.\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/KMhcm3\" target=\"_blank\">(more...)</a>\n</p>\n<p>\n	<strong>Do I have to play every day?</strong><br />\n	No, you do not have to play every day, but the more you play and participate, the more CineBucks you can earn to exchange for Entry Tokens and other prizes.\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/MAwFbx\" target=\"_blank\">(more...)</a>\n</p>\n<p>\n	<strong>Can I stop playing at any time?</strong><br />\n	Yes, particpate as much (or as little) as you want, but remember, the more you play the better your chances of winning cool prizes.\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/L1nVHi\" target=\"_blank\">(more...)</a>\n</p>\n<p>\n	<strong>How long do the surveys / games take to complete?</strong><br />\n	Usually between 5 and 15 minutes. Generally, the longer the survey is, the more CineBucks you can earn.\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/HsvOXp\" target=\"_blank\">(more...)</a>\n</p>\n<p>\n	<strong>What if I stop a survey in the middle of taking it? Do I still get credit? Do I have to restart it?</strong><br />\n	Once you start a survey you must complete it in order to earn your CineStars and CineBucks.\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/LniMKG\" target=\"_blank\">(more...)</a>\n</p>\n<p>\n	<strong>How often can I get CineStars/CineBucks for sharing??</strong><br />\n	For details on sharing, click here\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/MdZRSy\" target=\"_blank\">(more...)</a>\n</p>\n<p>\n	<strong>What are you doing with the information you are collecting?</strong><br />\n	We use the opinions and information you give us to (a) provide your\ncollective say-so to movie studio, producer & director clients to\nhelp inform their creative ideas for movies, marketing and other\nmovie-related content; and (b) provide say.so members with a better\nMovie Say.So experience!\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/OvqzVf\" target=\"_blank\">(more...)</a>\n</p>\n<p>\n	<strong>Can I trade my prize for another prize?</strong><br />\n	No, the prize you win, or redeem for, is the prize you get.\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/LniQtY\" target=\"_blank\">(more...)</a>\n</p>\n<p>\n	<strong>Can I track the status of the orders I have redeemed/won?</strong><br />\n	You will be sent a confirmation of your redemption or win. The delivery time of your item depends on the type of item you have redeemed or won. If you feel like there is a problem with your order, please contact us at movie@say.so.\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/JJPBOh\" target=\"_blank\">(more...)</a>\n</p>\n<p>\n	<strong>How do you select the winner(s)s for drawings?</strong><br />\n	You must redeem your CineBucks for Entry Tokens to be entered in the giveaways. Winners will be chosen at random from all entrants.\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/Kv1628\" target=\"_blank\">(more...)</a>\n</p>\n<p>\n	<strong>I am missing CineStars or CineBucks!</strong><br />\n	For missing CineStars or CineBucks\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/L7nqLX\" target=\"_blank\">(more...)</a>\n</p>\n<p>\n	<strong>I have a question that is not included in this FAQ!</strong><br />\n	You can check <a href=\"http://bit.ly/L1obWE\" target=\"_blank\">HERE</a> to see if there is an answer to a question that is not included in this FAQ. If you don''t see your question or answer, please feel free to send your question using the feedback section.\n</p>\n<p>\n	<strong>How do I contact someone?</strong><br />\n	We value our users feedback, concerns, and suggestions and want to hear from you. You can contact us by sending us feedback section of the bar, or by emailing us directly at movie@say.so. You can also use http://www.twitter.com/saysoapp or http://www.facebook.com/moviesayso to get in touch or send feedback.\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/KCKsgi\" target=\"_blank\">(more...)</a>\n</p>\n<p>\n	<strong>Where can I find the official Reward and Giveaway rules?</strong><br />\n	Links to the current Rules, Terms and Conditions, and Privacy Policies are all located at the bottom of the ''Edit Profile'' tab on the bar. You can also see them\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/Kv1k9i\" target=\"_blank\">here.</a>\n</p>\n<p>\n	<strong>How do I temporarily disable, or uninstall the Movie Say.So app?</strong><br />\n	Once registered, your account, CineBucks and content are always waiting for you, whether you have the app installed or not; but modern browsers are pretty slick now in letting us turn apps on and off without uninstalling them. You can leave Movie Say.So installed, and only activate it when you need it, or want to take advantage of a Movie Say.So offer, then deactivate it after you''re done. No more uninstalling and reinstalling! <a href=\"http://bit.ly/X0XyJO\" target=\"_blank\">Click here</a> link for further instructions on how to disable this app.\n</p>\n<p>\n	<strong>How do I remove the Movie Say.So browser app?</strong><br />\n	For Movie bar removal instructions...\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/MAxyAO\" target=\"_blank\">(more...)</a>\n</p>\n<p>\n	<strong>How do I link my Facebook or Twitter account?</strong><br />\n	You can check <a href=\"http://bit.ly/L7nnQk\" target=\"_blank\">HERE</a> for instructions on how to link your Facebook / Twitter account, or see below.\n</p>\n<ol>\n	<li>Click .Edit Profile.</li>\n	<li>Click to link your Twitter or Facebook account.</li>\n	<li>Allow access in order for the accounts to be linked.</li>\n</ol>\n<p>\n	<strong>How do I disconnect my Facebook / Twitter account from the Say.So bar?</strong><br />\n	You can check <a href=\"http://bit.ly/Lo1Y1W\" target=\"_blank\">HERE</a> for instructions on how to unlink your Facebook / Twitter account, or see below.\n</p>\n<p>\n	<strong>Facebook:</strong><br />\n</p>\n<ol>\n	<li>Log into Facebook.</li>\n	<li>Click on <em>Home</em> > <em>Account Settings.</em></li>\n	<li>Click on <em>Apps</em>. You will see <em>Say.So Bar</em> listed here.</li>\n</ol>\n<p>\n	<strong>Twitter:</strong><br />\n</p>\n<ol>\n	<li>Log into Twitter.</li>\n	<li>Click on your name > <em>Settings</em>.</li>\n	<li>Open the <em>Applications</em> tab and you will see the <em>Say.So Bar</em> listed here.</li>\n</ol>\n<br /><br />\n'),
