(49,5,12,'<h2 class=\"sb_title\">FAQ</h2>\n<p>\n	<strong>What is Social Say.So?</strong><br />\n	Social Say.So is a way to get rewarded for your opinions on social and casual gaming.  Members gain \"<strong class=\"sb_theme_textHighlight\"><big>Social SaySo</big></strong>\" (experience points) and \"<strong class=\"sb_theme_textHighlight\"><big>Social PaySos</big></strong>\" (currency). <strong class=\"sb_theme_textHighlight\"><big>Social PaySos</big></strong> can be redeemed for rewards and \"Entry Tokens\" into Social Say.So giveaways.\n	<a href=\"http://bit.ly/Rj3E6L\" target=\"_blank\">(more...)</a>\n</p>\n<p>\n	<strong>Do I have to pay for anything? Is there any shipping & handling fees for prizes obtained or won?</strong><br />\n	No, this is completely free to you. The only thing we want you to do is participate.\n	<a href=\"http://bit.ly/Y5Xuu0\" target=\"_blank\">(more...)</a>\n</p>\n<p>\n	<strong>What is </strong><strong class=\"sb_theme_textHighlight\"><big>Social SaySo</big></strong><strong> used for?</strong><br />\n	Social SaySo determines your level of influence and involvement. Gaining Social SaySo will increase your Social Say.So level. <a href=\"http://bit.ly/YrcnG7\" target=\"_blank\">(more...)</a>\n</p>\n<p>\n	<strong>What are </strong><strong class=\"sb_theme_textHighlight\"><big>Social PaySos</big></strong><strong> used for?</strong><br />\n	PaySos are the currency you earn by participating in polls, answering surveys, and sharing your ideas. In fact, virtually everything you do in Social Say.So will earn you PaySos. These PaySos can be exchanged for various prizes and Entry Tokens in the Reward Center. <a href=\"http://bit.ly/U2UcPp\" target=\"_blank\">(more...)</a>\n</p>\n<p>\n	<strong>What are Entry Tokens?</strong><br />\n	Entry Tokens are your way of entering prize giveaways. Users that have purchased an Entry Token with their PaySos will be entered to win the giveaway. To view current giveaways click on the giveaway section of the bar.<br 