(151,3,38,'<h2 class=\"sb_title\" align=\"center\">Here''s What You Get.</h2>\n<p align=\"center\"><big>Give us your opinion on movies , celebrities, and what''s going on in Hollywood and you''ll earn CineBucks, virtual currency redeemable for prizes and opportunities.</big></p>\n<br />\n<ul class=\"sb_lineList\">\n	<li class=\"sb_img_prizes\"><strong class=\"sb_theme_textHighlight\">Great Prizes.</strong> Almost Almost everything you do as a Say.So movie buff earns you CineBucks. Use these to redeem prizes from the Rewards Center that are geared to movie lovers like you.</li>\n	<li class=\"sb_img_giveaways\">You can also exchange your CineBucks for <strong class=\"sb_theme_textHighlight\">entry tokens for our giveaways</strong>. Buy as many entry tokens for each giveaway as you want to increase your odds of winning.</li>\n</ul>\n'),
(152,4,38,''),
(153,5,38,'<h2 class=\"sb_title\" align=\"center\">Here''s What You Get.</h2>\n<p align=\"center\"><big>Help us better serve your Social needs and you''ll earn Social PaySos, virtual currency redeemable for prizes and opportunities.</big></p>\n<br />\n<ul class=\"sb_lineList\">\n	<li class=\"sb_img_prizes\"><strong class=\"sb_theme_textHighlight\">Great Prizes.</strong> Almost everything you do as a Say.So social buff earns you Social PaySos. Use these to redeem prizes from the Rewards Center.</li>\n	<li class=\"sb_img_giveaways\"><strong class=\"sb_theme_textHighlight\">A Chance To Win Prize Giveaways. </strong> Redeem your Social PaySos for entry tokens for our giveaways. Buy as many entry tokens for each giveaway as you want and increase your odds of winning.</li>\n</ul>\n'),
(154,NULL,39,''),
(155,3,39,'<h2 class=\"sb_title\" align=\"center\">Give Your Opinion, Share It and Earn!</h2>\n<p align=\"center\"><big>Your point of view and opinion are invaluable. Express yourself through fun polls and surveys, and earn points by rating videos.</big></p>\n<br />\n<ul class=\"sb_lineList\">\n	<li class=\"sb_img_polls\"><strong class=\"sb_theme_textHighlight\">Polls</strong> are quick hits of opinion we''d like you to share. Answer as many or as few as you''d like, and for each one we;ll drop a little something in your Movie Say.So wallet. Every day you''ll get new polls to show off your movie knowledge so be sure to check back often.</li>\n	<li class=\"sb_img_surveys\"><strong class=\"sb_theme_textHighlight\">Surveys</strong> are the big money opportunities. These are important efforts to gauge how we are doing, and we''ll make sure you are compensated accordingly.</li>\n	<li class=\"sb_img_quizzes\"><strong class=\"sb_theme_textHighlight\">Spotlight - </strong>Rate movie trailers and videos; share them to Facebook or Twitter and we''ll compensate you with CineBucks and CineStars. No purchase necessary.</li>\n</ul>\n'),
(156,4,39,''),
(157,5,39,'<h2 class=\"sb_title\" align=\"center\">Give Your Opinion, Share It and Earn!</h2>\n<p align=\"center\"><big>Your point of view and opinion are invaluable. Express yourself through fun polls and surveys, and earn points by taking fun missions.</big></p>\n<br />\n<ul class=\"sb_lineList\">\n	<li class=\"sb_img_polls\"><strong class=\"sb_theme_textHighlight\">Polls</strong> are quick hits of opinion we''d like you to share. Answer as many or as few as you''d like, and for each one we''ll drop a little something in your Say.so wallet.</li>\n	<li class=\"sb_img_surveys\"><strong class=\"sb_theme_textHighlight\">Surveys</strong> are the big money opportunities. These are important efforts to gauge how we are doing, and we''ll make sure you are compensated accordingly.</li>\n	<li class=\"sb_img_quizzes\"><strong class=\"sb_theme_textHighlight\">Spotlight - </strong> Challenge yourself and test your knowledge by taking fun missions, or share them to Facebook or Twitter. We''ll compensate you with Social SaySo and PaySos. No purchase necessary.</li>\n</ul>\n'),
(158,NULL,40,''),
(159,3,40,'<h2 class=\"sb_title\" align=\"center\">Welcome!</h2>\n<h3>We''ve designed the steps below to help you get oriented with Movie Say.So. If you find you need additional help, please don''t hesitate to <a href=\"mailto:movie@say.so\">contact us</a>.</h3>\n<p align=\"center\"><big>By becoming a member of Movie Say.So, you''ve achieved the level of \"Extra\", and you''ve also earned extra CineStars and CineBucks.</big></p>\n<br />\n<ul class=\"sb_lineList\">\n	<li class=\"sb_img_experience\"><strong class=\"sb_theme_textHighlight\">\"CineStars\"</strong> show the level of influence you''ve gained by sharing your expertise, experience and opinion. As you gain more CineStars your access to higher levels of influence on Movie Say.so will grow.</li>\n	<li class=\"sb_img_redeemable\"><strong class=\"sb_theme_textHighlight\">\"CineBucks\"</strong>  are almost as good as cash. Virtually everything you do earns you CineBucks, which can be redeemed for all types of goodies from the Say.So <a class=\"sb_nav_element\" rel=\"sb_popBox_rewards\" href=\"/starbar/content/rewards\">Rewards Center</a>.</li>\n</ul>'),
(160,4,40,''),
(161,5,40,'<h2 class=\"sb_title\" align=\"center\">Welcome!</h2>\n<h3>We designed the steps below to help you get oriented with Social Say.So. If you find you need additional help, feel free to <a href=\"mailto:social@say.so\">contact us</a>.</h3>\n<p align=\"center\"><big>By becoming a member of Social Say.So, you''ve achieved the level \"Spectator\", and earned extra Social SaySo and PaySos.</big></p>\n<br />\n<ul class=\"sb_lineList\">\n	<li class=\"sb_img_experience\"><strong class=\"sb_theme_textHighlight\">''Social SaySo''</strong> is the currency of influence. You get SaySo by sharing your expertise, experience and opinion, and your Social SaySo determines your access to increasingly important levels of access and influence.</li>\n	<li class=\"sb_img_redeemable\"><strong class=\"sb_theme_textHighlight\">''Social PaySos''</strong> are almost as good as cash. Virtually everything you do earns you Social PaySos, which can be redeemed for all manner of goodies from Say.So. (<a class=\"sb_nav_element\" rel=\"sb_popBox_rewards\" href=\"/starbar/content/rewards\">see the Rewards Center</a>)</li>\n</ul>\n'),
